{"tid":1757020,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"屯元天新任區議員 入一入嚟唔該","createTime":"2019-11-26T10:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T22:03:25.000Z","uid":4092,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"2c009e5ef5029276958908c390c4fde06d77867b","tid":1757020,"uid":4092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:07:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">屯元天</span></span>係區議會都掌握大部分議席<br />\n我諗第一樣要處理係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交通</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我諗住屯元天既手足又好 普通市民都好<br />\n我哋都忍撚夠 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵</span></span><br />\n<br />\nDKLM 依家黨鐵為咗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">分化</span>普通市民同示威者 <br />\n<br />\n特登停曬所有輕鐵等候時間 甚至輕鐵要用 8-15分鐘等<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">建議</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但屯元天最大問題係除咗輕鐵 無其他<span style=\"font-size: large;\">選擇</span><br />\n<br />\n其實 屯門/天水圍 來往已經要一架 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">巴士</span>/<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">小巴</span> <br />\n<br />\n因為要來往屯天 只係輕鐵西鐵一收皮就無得返屋企<br />\n<br />\n屯門： 區內增設更多小巴/巴士來回各條邨<br />\n<br />\n天水圍 : 唔洗講啦 區內輕鐵一收皮麻煩到仆街 <br />\n一定要增設邨巴來往<br />\n<br />\n元朗 :唔太熟 歡迎提供意見<br />\n<br />\n趁我哋控制到區議會大部分議席 希望可以好好把握今次機重整交通 唔想再依賴<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵</span></span>"},{"pid":"0b8b396ed1d092f908efd1e412f098d1f53a2dbc","tid":1757020,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:08:53.000Z","msg":"Twitter 戰線勿鬆懈！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756092\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756092</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=8860df84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"a78c22265c5b167b555aa6e94f974ab3dbdf7302","tid":1757020,"uid":200830,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:09:34.000Z","msg":"支持巴打 屯元天太依賴黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1908abd8950b41d51b1dc4fed6f7f2f77a408bdb","tid":1757020,"uid":157453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:10:11.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"d4ce15d824082f9a62ed7b90acee5bdce63868be","tid":1757020,"uid":64296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:10:25.000Z","msg":"要增設多d 屯元天之間嘅交通同各自區域嘅交通 <br />\n唔好俾黨鐵壟斷"},{"pid":"0ad934471d6b5cff8b4493c937df7d23dbdbe62b","tid":1757020,"uid":189157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:11:04.000Z","msg":"拆撚左輕鐵佢唔該<br />\n阻撚住地球轉<br />\n讓返啲路面出黎"},{"pid":"27347ebea64441a6266ccbdbd20b146be879c4d4","tid":1757020,"uid":187201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:11:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e78c8c31ef07fb2a0955ef0f2f8cd8b2ecd6cb2","tid":1757020,"uid":4092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4ce15d824082f9a62ed7b90acee5bdce63868be","tid":1757020,"uid":64296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:10:25.000Z","msg":"要增設多d 屯元天之間嘅交通同各自區域嘅交通 <br />\n唔好俾黨鐵壟斷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:11:20.000Z","msg":"依個就係屯元天交通問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.g